name: uw-freelancer.github.com
body:
WordPress freelancer plugin allows you to display your freelancer.com details and activities on your WordPress blog. This plugin activates a number of freelancer.com related widgets inside WordPress admin widgets section. You can drag and drop those widgets to display WordPress freelancer plugin functions.

Visit [WordPress Freelancer Plugin](http://bapml.com/wordpress-freelancer-plugin) website.
